Clerics who take the Dream domain are immune to sleep effects and are masters of sleep and dreams.

<b>Domain Special Ability and Bonus Spells</b>
- Immunity to sleep: The cleric is immune to sleep effects, much as elves are.

- The cleric gains access to the following spells at the specified spell level: <i>sleep (1), deep slumber (3), phantasmal killer (4), hiss of sleep (7).</i>.